{"tid":1741320,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭文傑事件證實咗一地兩檢有幾危險","createTime":"2019-11-20T09:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T11:28:51.000Z","uid":183983,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f21e5f1f110619b9f2a5b6960f7a3e5f2330a3a3","tid":1741320,"uid":183983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"西九龍站「一地兩檢」的安排引發了巨大爭議。這引發了巨大的爭議。香港的親民主派抗議者認為，中國公安在西九龍站的內地口岸區駐有人員，是不受歡迎的中國當局權力的延伸。<br />\n在出差回程途中，鄭文傑就是在香港西九龍高鐵站，被中國當局攔住。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-50484844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-50484844&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLKnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=53d539ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-50484844&h=5c037213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-50484844</a>"},{"pid":"019cdddc650e1e0a1f7b54fbfbcdbb31d8598454","tid":1741320,"uid":183983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:36:54.000Z","msg":"「今年八月被指涉嫌嫖娼，被內地行政拘留15日的英國駐香港總領館香港僱員鄭文傑，下午在個人社交網站發文，指今年8月<span style=\"color: red;\">在西九龍高鐵站過境時被截停及送往深圳</span>，交予相信是國安部門的秘密警察。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493490-20191120.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493490-20191120.htm&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLKnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=b19cac01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493490-20191120.htm&h=2fd6da7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493490-20191120.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b3983e13b3e266ab7d20243dd1530863e69faf96","tid":1741320,"uid":19369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a319f3a21b54d990fc5b35a7aff7ba0e10cc735b","tid":174